Thank you for using Petty, a pet services application provided by SoftThrive. Your privacy and the security of your personal information are important to us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and protect the information you provide when using the Petty app.

1. Information We Collect

Personal Information: When you use Petty, we may collect personal information such as your name, email address, location, and other details you voluntarily provide while using the app.
Usage Information: We may also collect non-personal information about how you interact with the app, including but not limited to log data, device information, and cookies.
2. How We Use Your Information

Providing Services: We use the information collected to deliver the pet services you request through the app.
Communication: We may use your email address to send you updates, notifications, newsletters, and promotional materials related to our services.
Improvement of Services: Analyzing usage patterns helps us improve our app, personalize user experience, and enhance our services.
3. Sharing of Information

Service Providers: We may share your information with third-party service providers who assist us in delivering our services (e.g., payment processors, delivery services), but they are obligated to maintain the confidentiality of your information.
Legal Compliance: We may disclose information in response to a legal request, enforce our policies, respond to claims, protect rights, property, or safety of ourselves or others.
4. Your Choices and Controls

Access and Correction: You can access and update your personal information through your account settings in the app.
Opt-Out: You can opt-out of receiving promotional emails by following the unsubscribe instructions provided in the emails.
5. Data Security

We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.

6. Children's Privacy

Petty is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy. We will notify users of any material changes through the app or via email.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or your information, please contact us at [Your Contact Information].

By using the Petty app, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.
